    "Name": "No-Dachi",
    "Details": "Apparently developed from units captured by the Lyran Commonwealth Armed Forces, this variant completely overhauls the weapons mix. The left arm carries a pair of Medium Variable Speed Pulse Lasers, a Medium Pulse Laser, and a Small Pulse Laser. The two side torsos are each equipped with a Small Laser, Medium Pulse Laser, and ER medium laser, while the head mounts an additional Small Laser. The Sword on the right arm has been replaced with a BattleMech sized Mace. A Guardian ECM Suite is mounted in the center torso to disrupt enemy command networks.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Melee Actuators</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.1</color></b>\n\n<color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limit: Left Lower</color>",
